                <p rend="flushleft">I. <hi rend="italic">Report by the Deputies</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Deputies’ Report on the Agenda of the Council’s proceedings (<gloss target="#t_CFM461">C.F.M.(46)</gloss> 116) was adopted.<note n="42" xml:id="d179fn42">The substance of <gloss target="#t_CFM461">C.F.M.
                            (46)</gloss> 116 is set forth in footnote 40, <ref target="#pg_528">p.
                            528</ref>.</note>
                </p>
                <p rend="flushleft">II. <hi rend="italic">Reparation from Italy</hi>
                </p>
                <p>Views were exchanged on the question of the reparation to be made by Italy.</p>
                <p rend="flushleft">III. <hi rend="italic">Next Meeting</hi>
                </p>
                <p>The Council agreed to hold its next meeting at 3 p.m. on Wednesday, 19th June,
                    1946.</p>
